50|$|<b>The</b> Royal Thai <b>Marine</b> <b>Corps</b> (นาวิกโยธินแห่งราชอาณาจักรไทย) are <b>the</b> <b>marines</b> of <b>the</b> Royal Thai Navy. <b>The</b> Royal Thai <b>Marine</b> <b>Corps</b> {{was founded}} in 1932, when the first {{battalion}} was formed {{with the assistance of}} <b>the</b> United States <b>Marine</b> <b>Corps.</b> It was expanded to a regiment in 1940 and was in action against communist guerrillas throughout the 1950s and 1960s. During the 1960s <b>the</b> United States <b>Marine</b> <b>Corps</b> assisted in its expansion into a brigade. <b>The</b> Royal Thai <b>Marine</b> <b>Corps</b> saw action on the Malaysian border in the 1970s, and has now been increased to two brigades.|$|R
